=== LABORATORY_RUINS ===
# id: 86
# title: The Ruined Laboratory
# chinese_title: 废弃实验室
# category: Wreckage
# mode: dungeon

Overturned tables, shattered specimen jars, and scorched walls tell the story of an experiment gone catastrophically wrong. Among the debris, a few intact data crystals and sealed sample containers might hold valuable research. Chemical smells linger despite the ventilation.

* [Recover the intact data crystals]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "验" (yàn) — experiment, to test
* [Carefully collect sealed samples]
  ~ gain_item("toxin_grenade")
  "瓶" (píng) — bottle, container
* [Search for the research leader's notes]
  ~ gain_radical("目")
  "察" (chá) — to observe, to investigate. Contains "目" (mù) — eye.
* [Scrap the lab equipment for parts]
  ~ gain_gold(20)
  "器" (qì) — equipment, instrument
